----- How To Run -----

1. Linux
	1.1 Copy all files in some directory say Project
	1.2 Go to Project Directory
	1.3 On the terminal run,
			$ python main.py

2. Windows
	2.1 Copy all files to some folder say Project
	2.2 Open main.py in Python 2.7x IDLE
	2.3 Click on Run this module

----- Implementations -----

1. Select encoding for input Language from the Menu
2. Opening input file and printing first line.
3. Print next line when Next Button is clicked.
	3.1 Open new input file if the file preopened gets over.
